# Day 4 â€“ User Management & Sudo

## Commands Learned:
- `whoami`: Check current user
- `adduser`: Create a user
- `su - username`: Switch user
- `usermod -aG sudo user`: Give sudo access
- `sudo apt update`: Run a command as root

## What I Learned:
Today I learned how to create new users, switch between users, and give sudo access. I understood the importance of user permissions in cybersecurity.
